<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(ت)</span> ,<span class="c5"> وَعَنْ أَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ رضي الله عنه قَالَ:</span> <span class="c1">" نَهَى رَسُولُ اللهِ صلى الله عليه وسلم عَنْ الدَّوَاءِ الْخَبِيثِ <span class="c2">(١)</span> "</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
